---
layout: base.njk
title: Contact NADAF - Paper & Cardboard Recycling
description: Contact us for a collection request, information about our paper and cardboard recycling services, or any other question.
permalink: /en/contact/
sitemapPriority: 0.8
sitemapChangefreq: monthly
---

<div class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Contact us</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">We are here to meet your recycling needs.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container page-content">
  <div class="contact-layout">
    <div class="contact-form-section">
      <h2>Send us a message</h2>
      <p>Fill in the form below for a quick request. We will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
      {% include "components/contact-form.njk" %}
    </div>
    <div class="contact-info">
      <h2>Our details</h2>
      <p>Feel free to contact us for any information request or to schedule a collection of your paper and cardboard waste.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <img src="/static/images/icons/icon-pin.svg" alt="" class="contact-info__icon" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true">
          <div>
            <span class="contact-info__label">Address</span>
            {{ contact.companyName }}, ZI Hanchir Mastora<br>Drean, El Tarf, Algeria
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <img src="/static/images/icons/icon-phone.svg" alt="" class="contact-info__icon" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true">
          <div>
            <span class="contact-info__label">Phone</span>
            <a href="{{ contact.phoneLink }}">{{ contact.phoneDisplay }}</a>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <img src="/static/images/icons/icon-mail.svg" alt="" class="contact-info__icon" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true">
          <div>
            <span class="contact-info__label">Email</span>
            <a href="mailto:{{ contact.email }}">{{ contact.email }}</a>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <img src="/static/images/icons/icon-clock.svg" alt="" class="contact-info__icon" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true">
          <div>
            <span class="contact-info__label">Hours</span>
            Sunday - Thursday: 08:00 - 16:00
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="contact-map">
        <h3>Our location</h3>
        <iframe
          src="{{ contact.maps.googleEmbedUrl }}"
          width="100%"
          height="300"
          style="border:0;"
          allowfullscreen=""
          loading="lazy"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
          title="NADAF location map">
        </iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
